<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12 m4 l3">
    <%= image_tag 'basil/portrait.png', style: 'width: 100%' %>
  </div>
  <div class="col s12 m8 l9">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2em; margin-left: 1rem">Hey, I'm Basil.</h4>
    <h2 style="font-size: 1.4em; margin-left: 1rem">I can help you visualize your characters and other pages.</h2>
    <p style="margin-left: 1rem">
      Normally, I'd create images based on what you've already written about your characters on Notebook.ai to
      create more accurate images. However, I can also generate an image for your character if you want to tell
      me a little about them below.
    </p>
    <p style="margin-left: 1rem">
      Want to create images for your existing characters on Notebook.ai?
      <%= link_to 'Get started here instead.', basil_path %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
